  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3444740/extras/b1e6b38189c07580297ac9ab558dac44.poster.avif?t=1743786114\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3444740/extras/b1e6b38189c07580297ac9ab558dac44.webm?t=1743786114\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore a world filled with unique challenges and obstacles! 💚 In <strong>Goo Hunter</strong> 💚, you play as a brave Slime treasure hunter who uses her unique abilities to overcome dangerous obstacles and solve intriguing puzzles. With her sticky hands, she skillfully launches herself, uncovering the best path to progress in her adventure.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3444740/extras/1310352c64b99c5a20addd06a466e647.poster.avif?t=1743786114\" width=776 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3444740/extras/1310352c64b99c5a20addd06a466e647.webm?t=1743786114\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3444740/extras/1310352c64b99c5a20addd06a466e647.mp4?t=1743786114\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🧩 <strong>Key Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Challenging puzzles that test your strategy and precision;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >50 handcrafted levels with meticulous attention to detail;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Vibrant and charming pixel-art style;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A fearless Slime wearing a cute hat.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎮 <strong>Innovative Gameplay:</strong> Use the Slime's sticky abilities to swing through levels, grab onto surfaces, and reach seemingly impossible places. With simple and intuitive controls, you’ll explore every corner of this world full of challenges and rewards.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3444740/extras/2e23dddc0b56ae8c791871d51681b592.poster.avif?t=1743786114\" width=800 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3444740/extras/2e23dddc0b56ae8c791871d51681b592.webm?t=1743786114\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3444740/extras/2e23dddc0b56ae8c791871d51681b592.mp4?t=1743786114\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3444740/extras/b1e6b38189c07580297ac9ab558dac44.poster.avif?t=1743786114\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3444740/extras/b1e6b38189c07580297ac9ab558dac44.webm?t=1743786114\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore a world filled with unique challenges and obstacles! 💚 In <strong>Goo Hunter</strong> 💚, you play as a brave Slime treasure hunter who uses her unique abilities to overcome dangerous obstacles and solve intriguing puzzles. With her sticky hands, she skillfully launches herself, uncovering the best path to progress in her adventure.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3444740/extras/1310352c64b99c5a20addd06a466e647.poster.avif?t=1743786114\" width=776 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3444740/extras/1310352c64b99c5a20addd06a466e647.webm?t=1743786114\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3444740/extras/1310352c64b99c5a20addd06a466e647.mp4?t=1743786114\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🧩 <strong>Key Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Challenging puzzles that test your strategy and precision;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >50 handcrafted levels with meticulous attention to detail;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Vibrant and charming pixel-art style;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A fearless Slime wearing a cute hat.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎮 <strong>Innovative Gameplay:</strong> Use the Slime's sticky abilities to swing through levels, grab onto surfaces, and reach seemingly impossible places. With simple and intuitive controls, you’ll explore every corner of this world full of challenges and rewards.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3444740/extras/2e23dddc0b56ae8c791871d51681b592.poster.avif?t=1743786114\" width=800 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3444740/extras/2e23dddc0b56ae8c791871d51681b592.webm?t=1743786114\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3444740/extras/2e23dddc0b56ae8c791871d51681b592.mp4?t=1743786114\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
